		</div>
		<div id="small about me">
			<div class="ml-[5vw] text-yellow-400 font-['Arial'] font-bold pt-[20vw] text-[3vw] mr-[5vw]">
				While you sit in this space you will be forced to hear me list out some of my favourite hobbies hobbies...
			</div>


			<div class="ml-[10vw] pt-[20vw] text-yellow-400 font-['Arial'] font-bold pt-[20vw] text-[4vw]">
				Coding
			</div>
			<div class="flex justify-end items-center">
				<div class="ml-[10vw] bg-[#574d87] px-[3vw] py-[3vw] pl-[3vw] rounded-[2vw] w-[40vw]">
					<img src="../../assets/coding.png" class="rounded-[2vw] w-[40vw]">
