					For coding I know a few languages,
				</div> 
				<div>
				I know html, css, python and Javascript. 
				</div>
				<div>
					I typically code in Godot which is a type of game engine that is in GDscript which has python syntax
				</div>
				<div>
					Currently my device runs linux but it is Gnome as I got Gnomed
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="thirdlast_box" class="pl-[21vw] pt-[8vw] text-black-800 font-['Arial'] font-bold text-[1.5vw]">
