					The amount of time I have been coding for in Hackclub:
				</div>
				<div id="time">
				</div>
				<div>
					Am I currently coding at this moment?
				</div>
				<div id="current">
				</div>
				<div>
					Do I need to take a rest:
				</div>
				<div>
					Yes
				</div>
				<div>
					Am I?
				</div>
				<div id="wadu" class="pb-[30vw]">
					check
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
